\family default
3)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The discretized irradiance 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{PAR}^{k}$
\end_inset

 is located at the top of each layer 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

, and three different choices are available according to the parameter 
\family typewriter
LightLocationFlag
\family default
