\begin_layout Standard
Zooplankton is subdivided into microzooplankton and mesozooplankton with
 2 sub-groups defined for each component:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
carnivorous mesozooplankton 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{i}^{(3)}$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
omnivorous mesozooplankton 
