\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
3d-state: this section is used for all the state variables, which are defined
 as being virtually three-dimensional.
 This means that they exist in the whole domain, be it 0-, 1- or 3-dimensional.
 An example of state variable definition is shown in Box 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
